. do ape_check.do 

. * Quick APE check: average partial effect of majordrg in probit and logit
. clear all

. set more off

. use "../data/AmEx.dta", clear

. keep cardhldr income age selfempl ownrent acadmos majordrg minordrg

. replace income = income/1000
